            <scopecontent id="aspace_8346f7e4577796acfa57fcd72fceaadb">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The materials in this series relate to grants or projects that the Policy Sciences Center sought funding for either as a direct participant or in its role as a clearing house for interested researchers. The largest amount of materials relate to Garry Brewer's research detailing provision of services to the handicapped in the mid 1970s. Although the documentation for each grant is different, the materials consist primarily of correspondence, applications, and reports.</p>
            </scopecontent>
